

5) We will Create a Persons Table & Add a Check Constraint that the Age Should Not be Negative
===============================================================================================


CREATE TABLE persons (
person_id INT,
first_name VARCHAR(50), 
last_name VARCHAR(50),
age INT CHECK (age > 0)
);



INSERT INTO orders (person_id, first_name, last_name, age) VALUES (1, ‘Raj’, ‘Sharma’, -5);

[ERROR 1054 (42S22): Unknown column 'person_id' in 'field list']









